DevOps – Easy Notes
🔹 DevOps Kya Hai?
DevOps ek concept + process hai jisme Development (Dev) aur Operations (Ops) team mil
kar kaam karti hain taake software fast, stable aur efficient tareeke se release ho.
👉 Simple line (INTERVIEW GOLD):
DevOps is a practice that combines development and operations to deliver software faster with
better quality.
🔹 Dev + Ops Samajh Lo
• Dev (Development): Code likhna (developers)
• Ops (Operations): Server, deployment, infrastructure manage karna
👉 Small company:
• Same log dono kaam kar lete hain
👉 Large company:
• Alag departments hote hain (Dev team + Ops team)
🔹 Real Problem (Before DevOps)
• Dev: “Code sahi hai”
• Ops: “Server issue hai”
❌ Blame game start
👉 DevOps Solution:
✔ Dono mil kar kaam
✔ Issue fast solve
✔ System stable
🔹 DevOps ke Benefits (Interview Important)
• ⚡ Speed → fast deployment
• 🤝 Collaboration → teamwork improve
• 📈 Productivity → zyada kaam kam time me
• 🎯 Quality → bug-free product
• ⚖ Load handling → better performance
🔹 DevOps Tools (Yaad rakhna)
• Git → code manage
• Jenkins → automation
• Docker → containerization
• Kubernetes → scaling
• Ansible → automation
• Linux → server base
👉 Interview Tip:
DevOps tools automation ke liye use hotay hain.
🔁 DevOps Lifecycle (Step by Step)
🔹 Dev Phase
1. Plan → kya banana hai
2. Develop → code likhna
3. Build → code compile (Maven etc.)
4. Test → bugs check
🔹 Ops Phase
5. Release → ready for deploy
6. Deploy → server pe daalna
7. Operate → run/manage system
8. Monitor → performance check
👉 Short Trick:
👉 Plan → Code → Build → Test → Release → Deploy → Operate → Monitor
🔁 CI/CD Stages
1. Version Control
• Code versions manage
• Tool: Git
2. Continuous Integration (CI)
• Code compile
• Testing
• Validation
• Tool: Jenkins
3. Continuous Delivery
• Code ready for deploy
• Tool: Maven
4. Continuous Deployment
• Production me auto deploy
• Tools: AWS, Docker
👉 Interview Line:
CI/CD ensures automated building, testing, and deployment of code.
🤝 DevOps Culture
• Collaboration → Dev + Ops saath
• Transparency → sab ko visibility
• Shared Responsibility → dono zimmedar
• Continuous Feedback → improvement
🧠 DevOps Mindset
• Automation pe focus
• Small updates (big changes nahi)
• Monitoring zaroori
• Always improve system
🌍 Real World Examples (Yaad rakhna 🔥)
• Netflix → daily deployments
• Amazon → automation
• Facebook → continuous deployment
